summary: A body slide 2 preset I made that I tried to get to look as close to Dmra as I could.Also this comes with female boy meshes that are from the preset the prest aside from tweaking as you see fit is mainly for refitting armor/clothes
descriptionHtml:
[size=2]This is a pereset that I modeled to look like (If not close to) Dmra at 100 weight while at 0 weight it is around d cup with slimmer hips for use with  Calientes bodyslide 2.

The file comes with the preset and female body mesh files.

Feel free to add pictures and use the preset and mesh in any files you like I feel dmra would be a nice edition to Skyrim.
[/size][size=4]
